quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,aur hum ne is ke baad is ki qoum par koi lashkar nahi utaara aur nah hum aُtarne walay they hi
  36,29,woh to sirf aik chngharh thi (aatsheen ) so woh ( is se ) nagahan bujh kar reh gay
  36,30,bundon par afsos hai ke un ke paas koi paighambar nahi aata magar is se tamaskhur karte hain
  36,31,kiya unhon ne nahi dekha ke hum ne un se pehlay bohat se logon ko halaak kardiya tha ab woh un ki taraf lout kar nahi ayen ge
  36,32,aur sab ke sab hamaray rubaroo haazir kiye jayen ge
  36,33,aur aik nishani un ke liye zameen murda hai ke hum ne is ko zindahkiya aur is mein se anaaj aُgaya. phir yeh is mein se khatay hain
  36,34,aur is mein khajoron aur angarro ke baagh peda kiye aur is mein chashmay jari kardiye
  36,35,taakay yeh un ke phal khayen aur un ke hathon ne to un ko nahi banaya to phir yeh shukar kyun nahi karte ?
  36,36,woh khuda pak hai jis ne zameen ki nabataat ke aur khud un ke aur jin cheezon ki un ko khabar nahi sab ke jore banaye
  36,37,aur aik nishani un ke liye raat hai ke is mein se hum din ko khech letay hain to is waqt un par andhera chhaa jata hai
  36,38,aur Sooraj apne muqarrar raste par chalta rehta hai. yeh ( khuday-e ) ghalib aur Dana ka ( muqarrarkiya howa ) andaza hai
  36,39,aur chaand ki bhi hum ne manzilain muqarrar kar dein yahan taq ke ( ghatte ghatte ) khajoor ki purani shaakh ki terhan ho jata hai
  36,40,nah to Sooraj hi se ho sakta hai ke chaand ko ja pakdae aur nah raat hi din se pehlay askati hai. aur sab apne apne dairay mein teer rahay hain
